comments: Allen (MEM) makes incidental hand on ball contact with Ayton (PHX) when he dislodges the ball.
Ayton (PHX) reaches in and makes contact to Morant's (MEM) front during the drive. Morant moves through the marginal contact and continues his drive.
Allen (MEM) maintains a legal guarding position on Paul (PHX) during the drive.
Morant (MEM) briefly places a hand on the opposite side of Bridges' (PHX) body and he immediately removes it. The contact is marginal.
Jones (MEM) swipes down and avoids making contact to Booker's (PHX) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) makes marginal contact with Morant (MEM) during his driving shot attempt.
Morant (MEM) establishes a legal guarding position when Paul (PHX) extends his forearm into Morant's front during the drive.
Booker (PHX) commits a take foul on Allen (MEM).
Ayton (PHX) could be deemed to be in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Bridges (PHX) makes marginal contact with Morant (MEM) attempting to take a foul.
Paul (PHX) commits a take foul on Allen (MEM).
Anderson (MEM) makes contact to Bridges' (PHX) arm that affects his put back shot attempt near the rim.
Booker (PHX) commits a take foul on Tillman (MEM).
